data.description: This home offers a range of practical features for your comfort and security. It comes pre-wired for a security alarm and video surveillance, providing peace of mind for you and your family. Natural light is abundant throughout thanks to a solar tube, and ceiling fans ensure year-round comfort. The living room features a fireplace with a Pellet stove insert, which can easily be converted to gas or wood. Outside, there's a covered patio for outdoor enjoyment, rain or shine. Tucked away in a peaceful cul-de-sac, this property also offers the advantage of lower property taxes. If you're seeking a comfortable, secure, and practical living space, 882 Coyote Court SE may be just what you're looking for.
